arts.ttl: Cameroon held to shock draw by Eswatini in World Cup qualifying
arts.sum: Unfancied Eswatini hold Cameroon to a 0-0 draw in African qualifying for the 2026 Fifa World Cup, while Tunisia continue their unbeaten start.
